</div>





      <a href="https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20210702-1163716" target="_blank"><img class="view-desktop lazyload  " data-src alt style="width:100%;" pinger-seen="true" src="https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/undefined" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></a>
